1
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:20,700
"The Emotion"

2
00:01:20,019 --> 00:01:21,394
Wake up and get some food first?

3
00:01:50,686 --> 00:01:51,727
You're heavy.

4
00:01:52,769 --> 00:01:54,727
I thought we were going to eat.

5
00:01:57,311 --> 00:01:58,352
Hold on.

6
00:01:59,352 --> 00:02:01,269
Can't I get a morning kiss first?

7
00:02:01,936 --> 00:02:02,936
Please?

8
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,977
How many times have I told you

9
00:02:07,644 --> 00:02:09,186
to let me brush my teeth first?

10
00:02:29,178 --> 00:02:30,178
Wow.

11
00:02:30,761 --> 00:02:32,553
You're so touchy.

12
00:03:48,173 --> 00:03:50,590
Hey, what are you putting on me?

13
00:03:51,131 --> 00:03:53,215
It's CK cream.

14
00:03:53,715 --> 00:03:54,923
The one I use every day.

15
00:03:55,256 --> 00:03:56,840
Let me try putting it on you.

16
00:03:58,131 --> 00:03:59,548
Don't use too much.
Not too much.

17
00:03:59,548 --> 00:04:01,441
- Just a little bit.
- That's enough, that's enough.

18
00:04:01,465 --> 00:04:03,131
Enough, that's way too much.

19
00:04:03,173 --> 00:04:05,506
- It's too much.
- Let's see. Where?

20
00:04:05,798 --> 00:04:06,923
See that? Go.

21
00:04:07,756 --> 00:04:09,673
- Wait, wait.
- Don't put it there.

22
00:04:13,256 --> 00:04:14,673
Enough, I already applied it.

23
00:04:15,131 --> 00:04:17,298
- Okay.
- Put more later. Let me breathe.

24
00:04:17,506 --> 00:04:19,006
It's a waste, that's enough.

25
00:04:22,351 --> 00:04:23,518
What are you doing standing here?

26
00:04:27,226 --> 00:04:28,226
Where did you go?

27
00:04:28,976 --> 00:04:30,226
Why didn't you come home last night?

28
00:04:31,393 --> 00:04:32,935
And why didn't you call me at all?

29
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,726
Why are you questioning me?

30
00:04:36,851 --> 00:04:38,601
I was out making money for you.

31
00:04:39,726 --> 00:04:40,851
Stop being so jealous.

32
00:04:41,851 --> 00:04:43,518
Jealousy doesn't feed us,

33
00:04:44,018 --> 00:04:45,101
you know?

34
00:04:49,976 --> 00:04:51,060
Let's go home.

35
00:04:53,143 --> 00:04:54,185
Wait.

36
00:04:58,101 --> 00:04:59,601
Since when do you use this perfume?

37
00:05:00,976 --> 00:05:02,851
You left me waiting all night.

38
00:05:03,976 --> 00:05:05,018
Or were you

39
00:05:05,060 --> 00:05:06,310
sleeping around?

40
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,810
We'll talk about this at home.

41
00:05:32,332 --> 00:05:33,457
This man

42
00:05:33,457 --> 00:05:34,749
is my comfort,

43
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:37,332
my safe zone.

44
00:05:37,832 --> 00:05:40,540
He gives freely without me asking.

45
00:05:41,249 --> 00:05:42,915
Since the first day we moved in,

46
00:05:44,540 --> 00:05:46,165
until today, Nat's love

47
00:05:46,165 --> 00:05:47,582
is still at one hundred percent.

48
00:05:48,499 --> 00:05:50,915
But why is my love for Nat

49
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,832
fading a little more every day?

50
00:06:26,999 --> 00:06:28,582
We've been together a long time.

51
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,040
Wow.

52
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,498
So many orders today.

53
00:07:35,082 --> 00:07:36,082
I'll give you a boost.

54
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:45,295
You can take over.

55
00:07:45,753 --> 00:07:47,170
I'll go deliver the orders myself.

56
00:07:47,962 --> 00:07:49,128
Hey, hold on, Shane.

57
00:07:49,628 --> 00:07:50,878
Why tire yourself out?

58
00:07:51,462 --> 00:07:52,795
Stay here, I'll go instead.

59
00:07:55,045 --> 00:07:56,337
Your good intentions...

60
00:07:56,878 --> 00:07:58,045
if they're too much,

61
00:07:58,462 --> 00:08:00,170
they just become a burden.
Get it?

62
00:08:05,295 --> 00:08:06,170
Shane.

63
00:08:06,170 --> 00:08:07,850
- I can really just go myself.
- It's okay.

64
00:08:08,962 --> 00:08:10,087
Hey, wait, Shane.

65
00:08:10,503 --> 00:08:11,503
Give me a sec.

66
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,920
Wait for me, Shane.

67
00:08:18,087 --> 00:08:19,087
Shane!

68
00:08:20,545 --> 00:08:21,337
Shane!

69
00:08:21,337 --> 00:08:22,337
Shane, hold on!

70
00:08:28,378 --> 00:08:29,920
Safety first, okay?

71
00:08:33,878 --> 00:08:35,087
Stay safe out there.

72
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:36,729
Let me know when you arrive.

73
00:08:36,753 --> 00:08:37,753
Okay?

74
00:08:38,462 --> 00:08:39,837
I'm sick of how clingy you are.

75
00:08:40,962 --> 00:08:41,962
Bye.

76
00:08:42,628 --> 00:08:43,628
I'm leaving.

77
00:08:43,628 --> 00:08:44,628
Okay.

78
00:08:45,045 --> 00:08:46,045
Bye.

79
00:08:46,295 --> 00:08:47,295
Bye.

80
00:09:08,937 --> 00:09:09,937
Hi.

81
00:09:10,729 --> 00:09:13,187
Is the ring I ordered ready?

82
00:09:14,229 --> 00:09:15,895
Oh, it's ready?

83
00:09:16,604 --> 00:09:18,562
Okay, I'll go pick it up
this evening.

84
00:09:19,229 --> 00:09:20,229
Thank you so much.

85
00:10:10,691 --> 00:10:11,774
Where did he go?

86
00:10:15,149 --> 00:10:17,274
I saw him yelling out front
this morning.

87
00:10:19,524 --> 00:10:20,524
He's asleep.

88
00:10:23,649 --> 00:10:24,899
I'd be tired too.

89
00:10:25,691 --> 00:10:26,774
You never seem to find

90
00:10:26,774 --> 00:10:28,233
any good love.

91
00:10:30,441 --> 00:10:31,441
Honestly,

92
00:10:33,274 --> 00:10:34,649
you're great at everything.

93
00:10:35,524 --> 00:10:36,733
Even better than Nat.

94
00:10:37,066 --> 00:10:39,108
But the one thing I can't stand

95
00:10:40,524 --> 00:10:41,816
is how jealous you get.

96
00:10:44,274 --> 00:10:45,733
I've always believed that

97
00:10:46,358 --> 00:10:47,691
between two people in love,

98
00:10:49,066 --> 00:10:51,274
one will always love the other less.

99
00:10:53,683 --> 00:10:55,016
If you don't want to get hurt,

100
00:10:56,391 --> 00:10:57,516
you should be that person.

101
00:10:58,849 --> 00:10:59,849
Remember that.

102
00:11:00,308 --> 00:11:01,308
Just let it go,

103
00:11:01,599 --> 00:11:02,599
trust me.

104
00:11:38,139 --> 00:11:39,139
What are you doing?

105
00:11:39,681 --> 00:11:41,639
Your face is covered in dirt.

106
00:11:57,181 --> 00:11:58,181
Hey Nai.

107
00:12:00,514 --> 00:12:02,056
Remember where we...

108
00:12:02,556 --> 00:12:03,556
Uh,

109
00:12:05,014 --> 00:12:06,014
Oh,

110
00:12:06,889 --> 00:12:07,889
Of course I do.

111
00:12:11,973 --> 00:12:13,098
Want to go again?

112
00:12:30,203 --> 00:12:31,203
Sit tight.

113
00:14:28,984 --> 00:14:29,984
Fuck.

114
00:14:39,534 --> 00:14:40,492
You know,

115
00:14:40,492 --> 00:14:42,159
you're the person

116
00:14:42,325 --> 00:14:43,992
I want to be with all the time.

117
00:14:53,034 --> 00:14:54,117
But if that day,

118
00:14:54,825 --> 00:14:56,034
you hadn't broken up with me

119
00:14:57,075 --> 00:14:58,534
to date Nat,

120
00:14:59,617 --> 00:15:01,534
I wouldn't have to put up with Sak.

121
00:15:05,117 --> 00:15:06,367
Well, you were too jealous.

122
00:15:07,409 --> 00:15:08,409
It annoyed me.

123
00:15:11,284 --> 00:15:12,284
But whatever.

124
00:15:13,617 --> 00:15:14,617
No matter what,

125
00:15:15,950 --> 00:15:18,325
you're still my type.

126
00:15:28,075 --> 00:15:29,075
I...

127
00:15:31,409 --> 00:15:33,659
I think about you all the time.

128
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:37,780
Seriously,

129
00:15:39,322 --> 00:15:40,655
do you...

130
00:15:41,780 --> 00:15:44,488
do you still really love me?

131
00:15:50,363 --> 00:15:51,405
Of course I do.

132
00:15:54,113 --> 00:15:55,113
I love you a lot.

133
00:21:20,135 --> 00:21:21,135
What is this?

134
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:22,760
What is it?

135
00:21:35,427 --> 00:21:36,927
You said you broke up with him.

136
00:21:37,802 --> 00:21:39,385
Why are you still seeing him?

137
00:21:42,677 --> 00:21:43,677
I'm sorry.

138
00:21:52,927 --> 00:21:55,594
Shane, I'm begging you.

139
00:21:56,802 --> 00:21:58,135
If you really love me,

140
00:21:59,094 --> 00:22:00,677
you shouldn't cheat on me.

141
00:22:01,385 --> 00:22:02,385
Huh?

142
00:22:03,802 --> 00:22:04,802
Nat.

143
00:22:06,594 --> 00:22:07,594
The truth is...

144
00:22:14,927 --> 00:22:15,927
I don't love you.

145
00:22:18,526 --> 00:22:19,860
Hey, don't do this.

146
00:22:20,401 --> 00:22:21,401
Shane.

147
00:22:21,818 --> 00:22:23,276
I'm not mad at you anymore, okay?

148
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:25,485
I'll forget about today.

149
00:22:26,235 --> 00:22:27,485
But I just ask for one thing.

150
00:22:27,943 --> 00:22:29,223
Just love me like before, Shane.

151
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:31,110
Shane!

152
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:32,568
Love me just like before.

153
00:22:32,735 --> 00:22:33,943
- Shane.
- Listen to me.

154
00:22:35,776 --> 00:22:37,318
I could say it a hundred

155
00:22:37,901 --> 00:22:39,026
or a thousand times...

156
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,651
I really don't love you.
